{"tid":360813,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"IT狗們，見過最痴線既同事係點？","createTime":"2017-08-15T15:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T12:32:06.000Z","uid":72728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"886e663fc090ac9a45572268058749aee0bbecab","tid":360813,"uid":72728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:14:59.000Z","msg":"[好嬲,所以可能會1999] <br />\n有個做左一年同事既人，佢做野喇西又亂黎，寫code永遠都唔諗下家點接，亂9咁寫就算，寫完勁多bug，最後比個客屌公司，公司炒撚左佢。<br />\n佢個人本身都痴線，好撚鍾意睇哂同事們既所有fb ig，跟住cap圖share出黎。<br />\n自己fb開post又自己回自己。跟住好鍾意偷睇你個mon跟住再r水吹，但根本冇人想同佢講野。屌9佢又語無倫次，又拉開話題又話自己已經好克制又呢又路。<br />\n而家炒左半個月都未搵工，成日都響我地公司個wtsapp group度r水吹，迫人屌9佢。講真呢條友無論工作能力定係個人性格都差到極點，生平都未試過咁討厭一個人，岩岩條友又響group度r水吹，今次tag9我。<br />\n<br />\n認真如果有it公司in人既人睇左呢個post，可以pm我，我話你知佢個名，佢已經比人炒撚左兩次，真係唔好中伏。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩同佢嘈話佢歧視人佢又唔撚認，我到而家都仲好撚火滾！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de3d373c6805e95aa95c0aad96335d50524c9b3","tid":360813,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"真心膠一個o者，少動氣"},{"pid":"6f48e2a2dd28f1ddd2948bd6719d8ae47e06ef00","tid":360813,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c54791893c0c91c4f14f165be2d434c5dca9d7c",